{"tid":2448422,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"16歲白俄正妹通7國語言首選來台　感謝「台灣便當救我」","createTime":"2021-03-16T02:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T09:53:04.000Z","uid":16659,"like":152,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"ec35d5013cee6d530980f2cc6eefc77d7d7ffc2e","tid":2448422,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:03:04.000Z","msg":"今年僅16歲的正妹王瑪麗（Marika Wang）來自白俄羅斯，目前在台灣當模特兒，已經學會講7國語言，學習力驚人。王瑪麗透露，14歲離開白俄羅斯時，第一個選擇的國家就是台灣，而她最感謝的就是台灣便當「真的救了我」，十分好吃也不用擔心三餐要吃什麼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/16/3066993-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F16%2F3066993-PH.jpg&h=4f0e3ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王瑪麗14歲離開白俄羅斯時，第一個選擇就是台灣。（圖／翻攝自不要鬧工作室YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n「不要鬧工作室」上傳一段影片《白羅斯女孩14歲離家來台》到YouTube，王瑪麗提到，知道自己在白俄羅斯是沒有未來，因此「一直在尋找可以離開的機會」，她在14歲時就離開白俄羅斯，首選就是來台灣，當時只會說一點點中文，仍決定來台當模特兒。<br />\n<br />\n由於語言問題，王瑪麗沒辦法在片場自己點東西吃，因此都是跟著大家一起吃便當。王瑪麗回憶，廠商問她主食要選擇什麼肉，當她一次拿到便當時，裡面竟然有肉、青菜、飯和豆腐，相當擔心是否要多付錢，「因為我只有點雞肉啊，我錢也沒有帶很多」，後來得知廠商都會幫忙叫便當，因此她幾乎天天吃。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/16/3066995-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F16%2F3066995-PH.jpg&h=a7bbf6a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王瑪麗大讚台灣便當，「便當真的救了我」。（圖／翻攝自不要鬧工作室YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n王瑪麗感謝台灣的便當文化，大讚超方便又好吃，「我覺得便當真的救了我，因為我在工作的時候不用擔心要吃什麼」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/16/3066994-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F16%2F3066994-PH.jpg&h=66352967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王瑪麗已經學會講7國語言。（圖／翻攝自不要鬧工作室YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n目前16歲的王瑪麗已經學會講7國語言，包括俄文、白俄羅斯語、烏克蘭語、英文、中文、日文以及韓文。王瑪麗坦言會想念家鄉、家人，但也希望自己能在台灣待久一點，因為在白俄羅斯平均月薪僅約新台幣4000元，她的夢想是返回家鄉買一間公寓送給家人，「在台灣比較有機會能完成夢想。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/16/3066996-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F16%2F3066996-PH.jpg&h=3e5990a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王瑪麗夢想是返回家鄉買一間公寓送給家人。（圖／翻攝自Marika Wang IG）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BvIxT_UFdII\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBvIxT_UFdII&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirKzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=686cccfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BvIxT_UFdII</a>"},{"pid":"74e7416739bb4c8ca16704dd8d3f478b11daf5d0","tid":2448422,"uid":261849,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:05:07.000Z","msg":"依家賺咗幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2791707c410308b5bea1d5235b59e0450573a7a4","tid":2448422,"uid":49269,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:07:53.000Z","msg":"2年時間7種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2874fe0bd1cbc5af1eefc2566a7fd030bd0edb","tid":2448422,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2791707c410308b5bea1d5235b59e0450573a7a4","tid":2448422,"uid":49269,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:07:53.000Z","msg":"2年時間7種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:16:44.000Z","msg":"語言天才<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71808953238ecb2a711de9cb38664c5d5a7dd146","tid":2448422,"uid":27915,"like":12,"dislike":94,"score":-82,"quote":{"pid":"1f2874fe0bd1cbc5af1eefc2566a7fd030bd0edb","tid":2448422,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2791707c410308b5bea1d5235b59e0450573a7a4","tid":2448422,"uid":49269,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"r