%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F16%2F3066995-PH.jpg&h=a7bbf6a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王瑪麗大讚台灣便當，「便當真的救了我」。（圖／翻攝自不要鬧工作室YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n王瑪麗感謝台灣的便當文化，大讚超方便又好吃，「我覺得便當真的救了我，因為我在工作的時候不用擔心要吃什麼」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/16/3066994-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F16%2F3066994-PH.jpg&h=66352967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王瑪麗已經學會講7國語言。（圖／翻攝自不要鬧工作室YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n目前16歲的王瑪麗已經學會講7國語言，包括俄文、白俄羅斯語、烏克蘭語、英文、中文、日文以及韓文。王瑪麗坦言會想念家鄉、家人，但也希望自己能在台灣待久一點，因為在白俄羅斯平均月薪僅約新台幣4000元，她的夢想是返回家鄉買一間公寓送給家人，「在台灣比較有機會能完成夢想。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/16/3066996-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F16%2F3066996-PH.jpg&h=3e5990a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王瑪麗夢想是返回家鄉買一間公寓送給家人。（圖／翻攝自Marika Wang IG）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BvIxT_UFdII\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBvIxT_UFdII&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirKzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=686cccfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BvIxT_UFdII</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:38:17.000Z","msg":"16歲就咁既樣<br />\n30歲果陣咪阿婆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d2a497d2991d7ab7b074d42177d6945f0ca5bd","tid":2448422,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e173a82658da117f50a8dcb3fa3cd84534dbbc41","tid":2448422,"uid":3189,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:32:31.000Z","msg":"請佢食火車便當"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:40:08.000Z","msg":"唔值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3028666e86af6e08403ddf16edff73aec09ba58","tid":2448422,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9a0337e7f94c1f187ed7e348671ec6f1c4399951","tid":2448422,"uid":296231,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":