\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBvIxT_UFdII&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirKzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=686cccfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BvIxT_UFdII</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:38:17.000Z","msg":"16歲就咁既樣<br />\n30歲果陣咪阿婆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:40:25.000Z","msg":"鬼妹係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3bd76b9194f187f432e762b3a3f637ca5be8be4","tid":2448422,"uid":48074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:44:43.000Z","msg":"30歲過後變坦克<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4a57a56da397310dac20a5b98609091cd5c15a","tid":2448422,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b711e43dadbcd40192193b91dd095458c75e289e","tid":2448422,"uid":243175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:35:37.000Z","msg":"16<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:46:27.000Z","msg":"似26<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8231b5ad537e86d7ca85ef1fc514a7452c8b3f","tid":2448422,"uid":103230,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:48:13.000Z","msg":"以俄妹黎講<br />\n唔正"},{"pid":"821bac3ff447dac969f83631da9d880e7c6d8328","tid":2448422,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:50:18.000Z","msg":"佢睇得好開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54857976e119fb765b8a35c47ef91f85e26dcc2f","tid":2448422,"uid":49316,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"39bc2ad088c7e2a9e60b00f1884ee09fef9492bc","tid":2448422,"uid":283700,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score